858
01:04:24,777 --> 01:04:27,655
Right. Did his farts smell bad?

859
01:04:27,738 --> 01:04:30,116
No. They were just really loud.

860
01:04:31,784 --> 01:04:34,537
-Like this?
-Hey!

861
01:04:34,620 --> 01:04:37,748
I wanted to see
if my farts would be too loud for you.

862
01:04:38,416 --> 01:04:39,959
