866
01:05:05,818 --> 01:05:08,154
It's steamed just right.
It's not too tough to chew.

867
01:05:15,286 --> 01:05:18,039
Would you like some sake
to help you sleep better?

868
01:05:22,043 --> 01:05:24,462
Cheer up. For my sake.

869
01:05:25,963 --> 01:05:27,506
If you don't, I…

870
01:05:30,468 --> 01:05:31,552
Okay.

871
01:05:34,597 --> 01:05:36,432
I should get you some Oriental medicine.

872
01:05:36,933 --> 01:05:38,059
Let's get some tomorrow.

873
01:05:39,018 --> 01:05:41,729
-Are you free again tomorrow?
-I can always make time.

874
01:05:42,229 --> 01:05:43,481
After all, I'm my own boss.

875
01:06:25,106 --> 01:06:28,109
Your husband is cheating on you.

876
01:06:28,693 --> 01:06:30,778
Others can't possibly know
about other couples.

877
01:06:30,861 --> 01:06:32,989
There's something sly about Dongmi.

878
01:06:33,072 --> 01:06:36,325
